    "description": "<strong>Harmless Lies</strong> is a short but captivating 3D Visual Novel about learning from your mistakes and becoming the best version of yourself.<br><br>You play as <strong>Yui Shiraishi</strong>, a 16-year-old girl who transferred to a new high school in hopes of escaping the cycle of bullying she was stuck in.<br>The headmaster assured you that this would not repeat here... but so many things can go wrong, even on the first day!<br>You can feel everyone's eyes on you, judging your every move. <br>And just when things are finally starting to look up... you meet <i>her</i>.<br><br>Can you clear your name and expose the truth before it's too late?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get to know and befriend a diverse cast of characters.<br></li><li>Explore multiple detailed 3D environments.<br></li><li>Sneak around and cause distractions to avoid tense situations.<br></li><li>Practice with the cheerleaders via a rhythm minigame.<br></li><li>Try your best to resolve any conflicts and keep everyone happy.<br></li><li>Make the right choices to unlock one of four endings.</li></ul>",
